summary: This appears to be an email forwarding an FBI 302 interview report from an Assistant United States Attorney in the Southern District of New York. The subject line suggests it was intended to be read on a train, and multiple versions of an interview report are attached.

keyFacts: An FBI 302 interview report was being circulated among prosecutors in the Southern District of New York on September 17, 2021.
The email subject 'To read on train' suggests the document was being reviewed during travel.
Multiple versions of an interview report were attached to the email, indicating possible revisions or different formats.
The document identifier EFTA00076165 is associated with this communication.
